social_posts.post_text: My favorite of the themed minis I did this year — every single year I’m blown away by the bookings and how many of you want me to capture y’all! I’m so lucky to call this my job ✨

Midnight post bc it’s what I’m best at 😂😂😂 I just had to share the most special elopement at the most gorgeous greenhouse everrrr!! I will never get tired of photographing y’all’s love ✨

I’m also almost ALL caught up on all sessions taken this year! Thank you again to everyone who chooses me every single year and supports me. I love you all so much. 🤍
My absolute FAV time of the year ✨
So excited for these two 🤍

The sweetest couple celebrated their engagement with me 🤍 Aren’t they freaking perfect???? We also had one of the most gorgeous days we’ve had in a while. I cannot wait for their wedding next year, it’s going to be beautiful. 

~ also I will be releasing Valentine’s Day minis tomorrow so stay tuned 😍

Just a little magic ✨ Happy Thursday 🤍
Just some mountain wedding vibes for your feed this mornin’ ~ how UNREAL 😍
Senior portraits for this babe ~ isn’t she gorgeous?!! I’m starting to love these sessions so much! Tellll alll ya friends, now until May if you book a senior session with me you get HALF off 🤍
Just some bridal boudoir with this babe and I’m obsessed. Moreeeee boudoir sessions plz!! 🤍

Cowboy take me away… or however that song goes 🎶😍

One of my favorite sets of my boys and our mornings together. They have already changed so much and I can’t take it! Book the session, take the pictures… they are forever 🫶🏼
I haven’t shot outdoor before 4 pm in harsh light in idk how long, but this shoot is making me reconsider 😅 how freakin cute are these two??? Sometimes the last min shoots are the best ones 🫶🏼
It’s A R T ✨🫶🏼
Happy Easter, He is risen ✨🤍
Midnight post again 🤪 been so so busy lately and I couldn’t be anymore BLESSED. We have been making absolute magic over here y’all ✨

Talk thirty to me 🤠 Happy birthday to me!!! Cannot believe I am freaking 30, and how else better to celebrate than these?! 🫶🏼 thank you God for everything you have done and continue to do for me. Ready for this next decade of life, going to be the BEST yet. 🖤 and thank you to @ashlynbrookephotography for snapping these last minute AF for me to be able to edit with my vibe! Love you so much!!! 🫶🏼

Book the session with your mom or dad! You won’t regret it, pictures last FOREVER. ❤️

Both of these humans are some of my best friends, never met but had an absolute BLAST and I’m pretty sure I’m now a match maker 😇
